column5: [this morning headed off to barrie to meet up with my brother(misfish) he took me out fishing don't get out on the water much so when asked to go i jump all over it once we where out there it didn't take long for my bro to start catching fish   i was not doing so well but once i started to listing to my brother and useing tubes well the was the it nothing to big but it was all fun my brother did get him self a large mouth thanks alot brian
Good way to spend the day memart  Maueen
Anytime Rob anytime.You sure caught on on how to put the hurt with that tube. Im thinking a nuc plant trip soon.
good report Brian's getting to be a pretty good guide service..soon he's going to start charging for his expertise

Terry Im no wheres near that,I just like to get out and catch and have fun.Do,n that guide thing, I,ll leave that to the ones that can do it.  It,s all about fun for me as you and I both know.  Back to work Monday after 8 of 9 days on the water. Boy, do I need the break.LOL
